title: november 5: remember the fifth of november
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia remembers, remembers, the fifth of November. That’s right, it’s time for the history of Guy Fawkes day on the pod. To top it off, Maia explains how we got the phrase ‘Elvis has left the building.’ Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
